*******************************************************************************
       Name: Ledger Mark
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_IGNORE
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 12
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: ledger mark
   Wear-Off: !Ledger Mark!
Acquisition:
   - Cleric: level 14
Description:
   Ledger Mark is a Cleric utility spell that inscribes a divine tracking
   mark on a target in the name of Disk's accounting. The marked target is
   registered in Disk's divine ledger, allowing the Cleric to locate them
   or be aware of their presence. The spell is used for tracking enemies
   of the faith, marking those who owe divine debts, or maintaining
   awareness of important individuals.

   While the mark is active, the Cleric gains enhanced perception regarding
   the marked target and may have improved accuracy when targeting them with
   subsequent spells. The Ledger Mark represents the Cleric's role as a
   keeper of divine accounts — one who tracks and records all transgressions
   and debts on behalf of their god.
*******************************************************************************
